data.description: Beautiful home on a lake for sale. This beauty offers 4 bedrooms 2 full bathrooms, a family room, formal dinning room and great open kitchen complete with a pantry. The interior of this home features over 2,200 square feet of living space. It is bright and open, in excellent condition with view from most windows. There is fresh paint and flooring in most areas of the house. You can sit and look over Lake Wainani from your deck across the front yard. You can launch your water toys from your own concrete boat ramp & park your toy at your own dock. These are the beauties of living on a private lake. This property is just over 2 acres of your own space. There is an electric gate at the entry to the property.  The over-sized detached 3 car garage is more than a garage, it has a work shop across the back and an extra room along the one side, it could easily be made into a 4 car. The owners of this home put lots of love and great craftsman ship into this space and it shows. Come imagine what it's like to live on a lake. Don't forget to bring your off roads vehicles, too.
